 e Happy Ending</em> tells the deeply human story of a chance encounter tha
 t sparks connection\, adventure\, and maybe even love. Helmed by Tony Awar
 d-winning director Michael Arden (<em>Parade</em>)\, <em>Maybe Happy Endin
 g</em> has been called &ldquo\;Astonishing. Joyful\, heartbreaking\, cutti
 ng edge. Brilliantly executed.&rdquo\; (<em>The New York Times</em>) and "
 one of the most visually stunning shows to hit New York in ages" (<em>USA 
 Today</em>).&nbsp\;<br /><br />Don't miss the show that&rsquo\;s loaded wi
 th love\, <em>Maybe Happy Ending</em>!</p>
LOCATION:Belasco Theatre\, 111 West 44th Street\, New York NY 10036
END:VEVENT
